org.fcrepo.connector.fedora3

Interface FedoraObjectRecord

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFedoraObjectRecord, ObjectProfileObjectRecordImpl

    public interface FedoraObjectRecord
    An interface that exposes information about an object in Fedora 3. Implementations may vary about how they determine this information, but all methods are expected to be implemented such that they return meaningful values. All metadata is reprsented here, even those fields that are meaningless in the Fedora 4 architecture.
    Author:
    Michael Durbin
